OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1958FThe first edition of The Black
OL,7,Fand White Minstrel Show airs on BBC TV.
OL,8,
OL,9,CG1968FThe first edition of The Basil
OL,10,FBrush Show airs on BBC One. Having
OL,11,Fappeared previously on ITV and BBC
OL,12,Fshows, Basil Brush finally gets his own
OL,13,Fshow. Basil (Ivan Owen) was partnered
OL,14,Fon the first series by actor Rodney
OL,15,FBewes (or "Mr Rodney"). The show was
OL,16,Fscripted by George Martin and produced
OL,17,Fby Johnny Downes.
