OL,9,CG1996FTop of the Pops moves to Friday
OL,10,Fnights (7.30pm for one week due to
OL,11,Ffootball; 7pm would be the new, regular
OL,12,Ftime), having occupied a peak-time slot
OL,13,Fon Thursday evenings since 1964.
